  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The 100 core gameplay modes of war have multiple different and interesting modes, matched with multiple maps, weapons, and random performance, making every round a novel and exciting experience for you</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Numerous interesting and diverse rules</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Multiple weapons</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Various types of maps</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Interesting storyline experience</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The seven major levels allow for unlimited growth</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Explosive shooting pleasure</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The male and female leads are the only remaining human protagonists in this world. The male lead shoulders the responsibility of continuing human civilization, while the female lead is determined to seek revenge. The fate of robots and humans is the same</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164560/extras/fa3aebac03798b8a68eb4c88e5187f2c.poster.avif?t=1728995155\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164560/extras/fa3aebac03798b8a68eb4c88e5187f2c.webm?t=1728995155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164560/extras/fa3aebac03798b8a68eb4c88e5187f2c.mp4?t=1728995155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164560/extras/a1e42e5a62ac95abf5990af6f3b5e4e8.poster.avif